        {
            "title": "三花智控暗盤曾跌逾一成，現跌約半成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">三花智控(02050)暗盤早段大跌，輝立暗盤一度跌逾15%，低見19元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"三花智控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/002050-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"三花智控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/002050-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">三花智控官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">三花智控上限定價，招股價22.53元，輝立暗盤最低見19元，最高報23.6元，升4.75%，現報21.45元，跌4.79%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">耀才暗盤最低見19.98元，跌11.32%，最高見24.85元，升10.3%，現跌5.46%，報21.3元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">致富證券最低價見15元，踌3.42%，現跌5.02%，報21.4元。</p>\n</div>",
