        {
            "title": "大摩指本港樓市見底  預計下半年樓價升2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">摩根士丹利預期，香港住宅房地產市場在經歷了7年的低迷之後將見底回升，預計下半年樓價升2%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250429_PP_HK-PROPERTY_BP_1200.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250429_PP_HK-PROPERTY_BP_1200.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該行發表報告稱，受中國大陸買家湧入、資本市場改善以及利率下調的推動，香港房價即將觸底反彈，進入4 至5年的上升周期。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大摩指，內地買家推動香港樓市，香港的租金收益率現已超過內地一線城市，刺激了投資需求的成長。此外，復甦的資本市場產生財富效應，進一步支撐樓價。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">較低的利率也支撐市場。香港1個月銀行同業拆借利率在上個月暴跌後，目前徘徊在3年來的最低水準。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">然而，該行指出，香港仍面臨許多挑戰，例如未售出單位庫存激增、負資產抵押貸款增加及失業率上升 ; 一些發展商負債沉重。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15026712-%e5%a4%a7%e6%91%a9%e6%8c%87%e6%9c%ac%e6%b8%af%e6%a8%93%e5%b8%82%e8%a6%8b%e5%ba%95-%e9%a0%90%e8%a8%88%e4%b8%8b%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e6%a8%93%e5%83%b9%e5%8d%872",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240110_CR_source-web_hk-property_fb.jpeg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-20 17:20:33",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中原CCL : 二手樓指數按周升0.02%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">二手樓價陷入膠着狀態，反映主要大型屋苑二手住宅樓市走勢的中原城市領先指數(CCL)最新報135.6點，按周微升0.02%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">這是5月26日黃竹坑滶晨首輪91伙招標，30日中美貿易糾紛再度升溫，31日沙田UNI Residence首輪價單開售100伙，啟德THE HENLEY減價銷售80伙當周市況。CCL連續4周於135點水平窄幅爭持，最高135.6點，最低135.16點，上下波幅僅0.44點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中原地產研究部高級聯席董事楊明儀指出，拆息創新低，H按息回落，供平過租重臨，但一手新盤及貨尾繼續低開搶客，加上關稅政策未明朗，市場好壞消息參半，二手樓價陷入膠着狀態。第二季CCL有機會守住135點，暫時尚未跌穿財案前134.89點低位。至於近日以伊衝突加劇，股市反覆，美國放緩減息步伐的影響，將於7月的指數中反映。展望短期樓價走勢仍然偏軟，CCL的133點目標將推遲至第三季。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中原城市大型屋苑領先指數CCL Mass報137.01點，按周升0.2%；CCL中小型單位指數報135.67點，按周升0.12%。兩項指數齊升3周，分別累升0.59%及0.53%，同樣繼續於2016年8月底水平徘徊。CCL大型單位指數報135.21點，按周跌0.5%，連跌2周共0.92%，創2016年8月底後的逾8年半新低。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">四區樓價二升二跌。港島CCL Mass報133.17點，按周跌0.17%；新界東CCL Mass報153.36點，按周升1.7%；九龍CCL Mass134.57點，按周升0.43%，連升2周共1.12%。新界西CCL Mass報124.83點，按周跌0.91%，結束2周連升。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港島、九龍、新界西及新界東指數，分別處於2014年7月底、2016年9月中、2016年10月初及2017年2月中水平</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15026674-%e4%b8%ad%e5%8e%9fccl-%e4%ba%8c%e6%89%8b%e6%a8%93%e6%8c%87%e6%95%b8%e6%8c%89%e5%91%a8%e5%8d%870-02",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240726_PP_PROPERTY_INDEX_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-20 17:10:33",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全日收市｜港股收升292點  泡泡瑪特等捱沽  一周計科指跌逾2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股收市競價時段直線向上，最多升301點，升292點，一周計三指數俱跌，恒生科技指數一周跌逾2%，泡泡瑪特(09992)及同類股份大挫。中資金融股成升市主力。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數全日報23530，升292點或1.26%，今早報23291，升53點或0.23%，已為全日低位，隨即節節向上，午後早段區間上落，競價時段忽然急速向上，最高見23538，升301點或1.3%，為全日高位。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：布魯可官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241209_FI_source-web_Bloks-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：布魯可官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241209_FI_source-web_Bloks-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：布魯可官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"Shutterstock圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source_licensed_中國人壽_shutterstock_FB_1.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"Shutterstock圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source_licensed_中國人壽_shutterstock_FB_1.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">Shutterstock圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：海天味業招股書\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250611_FI_source-web_03288-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：海天味業招股書\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250611_FI_source-web_03288-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：海天味業招股書</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：布魯可官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241209_FI_source-web_Bloks-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：布魯可官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"Shutterstock圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source_licensed_中國人壽_shutterstock_FB_1.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">Shutterstock圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：海天味業招股書\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250611_FI_source-web_03288-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：海天味業招股書</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">一周計恒指累跌362點或1.52%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數全日升44點或0.88%，報5133點，今早開報5103，升15點或0.3%。科指一周累跌106點或2.02%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數全日報116點或1.38%，報8527點，今早開升18點或0.22%，報8429點。國指一周累跌128點或1.48%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指全日升   或257點，報23486，低水19點 ; 恒生科技指數升32點或0.63%，報5121點，低水3點，國指期貨升98點或1.17%，報8503點，低水12點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交2224.23億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泡泡瑪特(09992)全日跌3.62%，報239.6元，人民日報發文籲管制盲盒，此外公司主打Labubu在二手市場價格腰斬。同類股份布魯可(00325)瀉9.68%，報139.1元，創1個月新低，跌穿50天線(143.662元)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：布魯可官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241209_FI_source-web_Bloks-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：布魯可官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241209_FI_source-web_Bloks-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：布魯可官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">李寧(02331)全日漲4.8%，報15.72元，是表現最好藍籌，獲非凡領越(00933)增持，非凡領越全日升17.65%，報0.4元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中資金融股成升市主力。中國人壽(02628)升4.74%，報18.58元，升幅居藍籌股第二位；建設銀行(00939)升3.34%，報7.73元；中國平安(02318)升2.94%，報47.35元；工商銀行(01398)升2.82%，報6.2元；招商銀行(03968)升1.82%，報53.1元；中國銀行(03988)升1.57%，報4.54元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Shutterstock圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source_licensed_中國人壽_shutterstock_FB_1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Shutterstock圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source_licensed_中國人壽_shutterstock_FB_1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Shutterstock圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">信義系捱沽，信義玻璃(00868)跌3.82%，報7.06元; 信義光能(00968)跌2.11%，報2.32元，為表現最差兩藍籌股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">海天味業(03288)破底，收跌2.06%，報35.75元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：海天味業招股書\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250611_FI_source-web_03288-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：海天味業招股書\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250611_FI_source-web_03288-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：海天味業招股書</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15026547-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%bd%9c%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%87292%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b3%a1%e6%b3%a1%e7%91%aa%e7%89%b9%e7%ad%89%e6%8d%b1%e6%b2%bd-%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e8%a8%88%e7%a7%91",
